{"tid":2439030,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港台：英國通訊管理局據報向CGTN罰款22.5萬英鎊","createTime":"2021-03-09T03:01:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-09T03:01:19.000Z","uid":290404,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2cafb25c8906400318ee3651808a86ccd25ec9af","tid":2439030,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T03:01:19.000Z","msg":"罰左就罰左，無話據報唔據報，硬係加個「據報」兩字加埋最後果段提埋中共既回應擺明係唔gur<br />\n<br />\n英國通訊管理局<strong><ins>據報</ins></strong>向中國環球電視網(CGTN)罰款22萬5千英鎊。<br />\n<br />\n英國金融時報報道，英國通訊管理局以違反公平、隱私和公正性規定為理由，決定對CGTN處以罰款。<br />\n<br />\n英國通訊局上月吊銷CGTN在英國的廣播牌照，<strong>中國外交部表示堅決反對，敦促英方立即糾正錯誤。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1579531-20210309.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1579531-20210309.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=eGp%2FCvHI00KNC8mlo1Mhy95k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=6e481e64\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1579531-20210309.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=f81f734a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1579531-20210309.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"}]}